The paper is about natural language processing and specifically focuses on answer selection, which falls under the category of information retrieval (cs.IR) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of pre-trained models and deep learning techniques also suggests that it could fall under the categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), and computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CC).
